FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774811467
OL,3,CFarmer who allowed waste to be dumped
OL,4,Cand buried at beauty spot sentenced
OL,6,FOn follow up visits they found
OL,7,Fexcavators working on site and burying
OL,8,Fthe waste.
OL,10,FDespite formal warnings and a
OL,11,Fstatutory notice requiring the removal
OL,12,Fof all waste from the land, the
OL,13,Foffending continued for more than a
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe court found it was deliberate and
OL,17,Fsignificant, and sentenced Fortune to
OL,18,F12 months in prison, suspended for two
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
