FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774811467
OL,3,CFarmer who allowed waste to be dumped
OL,4,Cand buried at beauty spot sentenced
OL,6,FHe was fined #2,500 for breaching an
OL,7,Funrelated suspended prison sentence
OL,8,Fand will also carry out 20 days of
OL,9,Frehabilitation activity, pay costs of
OL,10,F#10,000 and a victim surcharge of #187.
OL,12,FFortune was also ordered to clear all
OL,13,Fwaste from the site within two years.
OL,15,FBen Hocking, Area Environment Manager
OL,16,Fat the Environment Agency, said he
OL,17,Fhopes the case sends a clear message
OL,18,Fto offenders.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
