PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774811467
OL,3,CFarmer who allowed waste to be dumped
OL,4,Cand buried at beauty spot sentenced
OL,6,F""Fortune's deliberate offending
OL,7,Fshowed a total disregard for the law,
OL,8,Fthe environment, and the community
OL,9,Fwhere he lives.
OL,11,F"I hope this sends out the message to
OL,12,Fothers that we are cracking down on
OL,13,Fwaste crime and we will take action
OL,14,Fagainst those who breach the law."
